Yewweḍ uḥemmal sanga ur yewwiḍ.
Ad d-slen asenda ur d-sellen.
Ɛeddi-d ad d-teṭṭfeḍ tummeẓt n waman.
Tenna-as tteryel: "Kullec rniɣ-t, ar ttṛebga terna-yi."
Seg wasmi i yurweɣ, ur ččiɣ lerbaḥ.
Seg wasmi i yurweɣ, ur ččiɣ ayen zeddigen.
Yenna-as uyaziḍ. "Anda yella llqeḍ yid-m a lalla?"
Ad tafeḍ iniɣman, anda ttqeggilent wulli.
Tuffra n uɣyul deg utemmun.
Ad d-yefk ugudu lexṛif.
Imdanen-agi, heddren kan.
Ur yettnecṛaḥ ḥedd d uɣyul-is.
Temmzel tixsi d yelli-s, yal yiwet tɛelleq seg ucekkab-is.
A yul yebḍan ɣef sin, yebɣa Ḥsen d Lḥusin.
Yiwen n wul yeqqar err akka, wayeḍ yeqqar err akkin.
Yeččur almi yettenɣal.
Ad yefk tunṭict i Ṛebbi.
Mi n-tufiḍ aɣezzfan yerwel, d awezzlan i t-id-iḍefren.
Ma ifat-ik wawal, ini-as sliɣ. Ma ifat-ik wučči, ini-as ṛwiɣ.
Win yeččan yečča, ma d wayeḍ teṛbut tekkes.
Lemɛenda n tnuḍin, yenɣan argaz ur yuḍin.
Yemma-s tneddaṛ yelli-s, tagujilt temmal i yixef-is.
Ulayɣer twessaḍ agujil ɣef yimeṭṭawen.
Tesmekta-d agujil ɣef yimeṭṭawen.
Ala win yewwten, d win yettewwten i yeẓran ansi i d-tekka tyita.
Ay amuḍin ma ad teččeḍ.
